repository-code: "https://github.com/ytrofr/claude-code-quest"
url: "https://github.com/ytrofr/claude-code-quest"
abstract: >-
  RPG-style project roadmap dashboard for Claude Code users. Renders central
  quests.json into themed HTML maps (Pokémon, Storybook), parses plan-file
  checkboxes for auto-progress, supports drop-in themes via folder-based
  contract. Zero LLM calls, zero external dependencies, localhost-only.
keywords:
